fer to a king’s assassination; Hb obscure."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 21:9","book":"Psa","chapter":21,"verse":9},{"label":"Hs 13:10","book":"Hos","chapter":13,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"These vv. may refer to a king’s assassination; Hb obscure."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Hos:7:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Ephraim has allowed himself to get mixed up with the nations."},{"kind":"text","text":" Ephraim is unturned bread baked on a griddle."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Hos:7:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Foreigners consume his strength, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:7","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but he does not notice. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 4:6","book":"Hos","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Even his hair is streaked with gray,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but he does not notice."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 1:7","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Hs 4:6","book":"Hos","chapter":4,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Hos:7:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Israel’s arrogance testifies against them, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit against his face"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 5:5","book":"Hos","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" yet they do not return to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" their God, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 5:4","book":"Hos","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and for all this, they do not seek him."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Hs 5:5","book":"Hos","chapter":5,"verse":5},{"label":"Hs 5:4","book":"Hos","chapter":5,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit against his face"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Hos:7:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Ephraim has become like a silly, senseless dove; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 4:6","b